To view QNN documentation, point your web browser to ${QNN_SDK_ROOT}/docs/index.html
   - e.g. firefox ${QNN_SDK_ROOT}/docs/index.html

To view information on setting up QNN SDK, point your web browser to ${QNN_SDK_ROOT}/docs/general/setup.html
   - e.g. firefox ${QNN_SDK_ROOT}/docs/general/setup.html

For help with QNN SDK tools, point your web browser to ${QNN_SDK_ROOT}/docs/general/tools.html
   - e.g. firefox ${QNN_SDK_ROOT}/docs/general/tools.html

To view QNN API Error Codes, point your web browser to ${QNN_SDK_ROOT}/docs/general/qnn_api_error_codes.html
   - e.g. firefox ${QNN_SDK_ROOT}/docs/general/qnn_api_error_codes.html
